Ok alot of people saying have alot of mana helps and I aggree or dissagree with that.<br>
Whether you have 1000 mana or 3000 mana you still gain it back a X per tick. Lets say x is = to 10. That means it takes 100 ticks to be FM with 1000mana or 300 ticks with 3000 mana. That means that if you are NEVER FoM your doing just as well with 1000 mana as someone with 3000 mana. Now if you are FoM you aren't burning mana fast enough.<br>
<br>
The truth is in any sustained killing enviroment having more mana means shit if you keep yourself from going FoM. Someone with 1000 mana can do JUST as good a job as someone with 3000. <p>Zurrin Zypher <BR>
