<br>
I'm at 220 unbuffed STR without focusing on STR gear and without having put any points into it.  I hit near max STR with a frost giant beard, let alone with a Shaman buff.<br>
<br>
Troll or Ogre SK should put starting points into INT if they plan to solo alot or STA if they don't.<br>
<br>
Max epic hit is 217 damage with max STR, 211 with my unbuffed STR, but my average parsed damage doesn't change by more than 5-10 damage per minute with max STR.<br>
<br>
Ogre makes the best tanking SK, but even they can't stand up to major tanking in the high level game.<br>
<br>
Troll makes the second best tanking SK and the best soloer, straight up to 60th.  The added regen really helps.<br>
<br>
Iksar makes a good soloer and sports the higher AC once they get into planar gear.  Starting with Fear Plane armor, their armor is as good or better than the other races.<br>
<br>
Heck, now at 56th, I can handle all of SS [Sol B] and the surrounding LDCs solo as fast as they can spawn.  It takes a really incredible group to get my exp faster than I can solo it. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernclassdiscussion.showMessageRange?topicID=84.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b> <a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernclassdiscussion.showMessageRange?topicID=84.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernclassdiscussion.showMessageRange?topicID=84.topic&start=61&stop=63>4</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernclassdiscussion.showPrevMessage?topicID=84.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernclassdiscussion.showNextMessage?topicID=84.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernclassdiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=84.topic&index=40><img src=http://members.cox.net/cbilyeu/tavern/notnice_reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernclassdiscussion.emailToFriend?topicID=84.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernclassdiscussion.threadControl?topicID=84.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/grunge/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernclassdiscussion.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=84.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of repli